{"blogid": "124848140", "writerAge": "码龄5年", "writerBlogNum": "120", "writerCollect": "1857", "writerComment": "122", "writerFan": "603", "writerGrade": "6级", "writerIntegral": "4571", "writerName": "我爱吃狮子头", "writerProfileAdress": "writer_image\\profile_124848140.jpg", "writerRankTotal": "15112", "writerRankWeekly": "39255", "writerThumb": "528", "writerVisitNum": "356490", "blog_read_count": "6930", "blog_time": "已于 2022-05-20 12:46:41 修改", "blog_title": "用VSCode编译运行C++（2022最新教程）以及会遇到的两个问题", "content": "<div class=\"article_content clearfix\" id=\"article_content\">\n<link href=\"style.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<div class=\"htmledit_views\" id=\"content_views\">\n<p>这玩意我弄了一下午，发现网上很多教程都过时了，现在自己整理一下造福后人。</p>\n<p id=\"main-toc\"><strong>目录</strong></p>\n<p id=\"%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD%E5%92%8C%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEmingw64%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%B3C%2FC%2B%2B%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91%E5%99%A8GCC%E7%9A%84Windows%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC-toc\" style=\"margin-left:40px;\"><a href=\"#%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD%E5%92%8C%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEmingw64%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%B3C%2FC%2B%2B%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91%E5%99%A8GCC%E7%9A%84Windows%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC\">第一步，下载和配置mingw64，即C/C++编译器GCC的Windows版本</a></p>\n<p id=\"%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E6%AD%A5%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD%E5%92%8C%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85VSCode-toc\" style=\"margin-left:40px;\"><a href=\"#%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E6%AD%A5%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD%E5%92%8C%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85VSCode\">第二步，下载和安装VSCode</a></p>\n<p id=\"%C2%A0%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E6%AD%A5%EF%BC%8C%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8CC%2B%2B%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81-toc\" style=\"margin-left:40px;\"><a href=\"#%C2%A0%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E6%AD%A5%EF%BC%8C%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8CC%2B%2B%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81\">第三步，编译运行C++代码</a></p>\n<p id=\"%E7%84%B6%E5%90%8E%E5%BE%88%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%BA%E8%BF%98%E6%98%AF%E4%BC%9A%E4%B8%8D%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%AB%E6%80%95%EF%BC%81-toc\" style=\"margin-left:40px;\"><a href=\"#%E7%84%B6%E5%90%8E%E5%BE%88%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%BA%E8%BF%98%E6%98%AF%E4%BC%9A%E4%B8%8D%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%AB%E6%80%95%EF%BC%81\">会遇到的问题</a></p>\n<p id=\"1.%23include%E6%8A%A5%E9%94%99%EF%BC%8C%E6%89%BE%E4%B8%8D%E5%88%B0%E5%A4%B4%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E3%80%82-toc\" style=\"margin-left:80px;\"><a href=\"#1.%23include%E6%8A%A5%E9%94%99%EF%BC%8C%E6%89%BE%E4%B8%8D%E5%88%B0%E5%A4%B4%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E3%80%82\">1.#include报错，找不到头文件。</a></p>\n<p id=\"%C2%A02.%E2%80%9Cg%2B%2B%20%3A%20%E6%97%A0%E6%B3%95%E5%B0%86%E2%80%9Cg%2B%2B%E2%80%9D%E9%A1%B9%E8%AF%86%E5%88%AB%E4%B8%BA%20cmdlet%E3%80%81%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E3%80%81%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E6%88%96%E5%8F%AF%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%E7%9A%84%E5%90%8D%E7%A7%B0%E3%80%82%E2%80%9D-toc\" style=\"margin-left:80px;\"><a href=\"#%C2%A02.%E2%80%9Cg%2B%2B%20%3A%20%E6%97%A0%E6%B3%95%E5%B0%86%E2%80%9Cg%2B%2B%E2%80%9D%E9%A1%B9%E8%AF%86%E5%88%AB%E4%B8%BA%20cmdlet%E3%80%81%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E3%80%81%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E6%88%96%E5%8F%AF%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%E7%9A%84%E5%90%8D%E7%A7%B0%E3%80%82%E2%80%9D\"> 2.“g++ : 无法将“g++”项识别为 cmdlet、函数、脚本文件或可运行程序的名称。”</a></p>\n<hr id=\"hr-toc\"/>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<h2 id=\"%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD%E5%92%8C%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEmingw64%EF%BC%8C%E5%8D%B3C%2FC%2B%2B%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91%E5%99%A8GCC%E7%9A%84Windows%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC\">第一步，下载和配置mingw64，即C/C++编译器GCC的Windows版本</h2>\n<p>1.官网下载：<a href=\"https://sourceforge.net/projects/mingw-w64/files/\" title=\"MinGW-w64 - for 32 and 64 bit Windows -  Browse Files at SourceForge.net\">MinGW-w64 - for 32 and 64 bit Windows - Browse Files at SourceForge.net</a></p>\n<p>或者百度云：<a href=\"https://pan.baidu.com/s/1DPr2ex1VDatAEP9Gg_4IJg\" title=\"https://pan.baidu.com/s/1DPr2ex1VDatAEP9Gg_4IJg\">https://pan.baidu.com/s/1DPr2ex1VDatAEP9Gg_4IJg</a> ，提取码：star</p>\n<p>2.解压到一个文件夹，比如我的：D:\\aaakkk\\cpp\\mingw64</p>\n<p>3.配置环境变量：直接点放大镜搜索环境变量：</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"302\" src=\"image\\7bcf6312f49644419e5930ed990369e4.png\" width=\"484\"/></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"590\" src=\"image\\e45d892ac9954c89949f28d62e1daa85.png\" width=\"515\"/></p>\n<p></p>\n<p> <img alt=\"\" height=\"501\" src=\"image\\49ae81807ab34736bdaf7980e671bcea.png\" width=\"513\"/></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"506\" src=\"image\\f964dfd8cf544f3aba4492df53c69678.png\" width=\"515\"/></p>\n<p> 把刚才解压的地址加上\\bin添加进去，比如我的：D:\\aaakkk\\cpp\\mingw64\\bin，然后点确定，<strong>注意一定要确保它被保存了。</strong>然后可以在控制台输入gcc -v，如果出来“不是内部或外部命令，也不是可运行的程序或批处理文件”那就是没成功。</p>\n<p></p>\n<h2 id=\"%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E6%AD%A5%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD%E5%92%8C%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85VSCode\">第二步，下载和安装VSCode</h2>\n<p>下载地址：<a href=\"https://code.visualstudio.com/\" title=\"https://code.visualstudio.com/\">https://code.visualstudio.com/</a></p>\n<p>下载安装没什么好说的，打开后安装这两个插件：<strong>C/C++、Code Runner（有了这个插件就不用像别的教程一样配置那些烦人的launch.json文件了！！！）</strong>，也可以再下个中文插件：<strong>Chinese (Simplified) (简体中文)</strong>，这样界面就成中文的了。安装完后重启VSCode以生效。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"221\" src=\"image\\d3c152f4420543f09df8a9a22a70571e.png\" width=\"524\"/></p>\n<p></p>\n<h2 id=\"%C2%A0%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E6%AD%A5%EF%BC%8C%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8CC%2B%2B%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81\">第三步，编译运行C++代码</h2>\n<p>新建一个文件夹，在里面新建一个.cpp文件，随便写点C++代码如:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-cpp\">#include&lt;iostream&gt;\nusing namespace std;\n\nint main(){\n    cout&lt;&lt;\"test\";\n}</code></pre>\n<p>然后点右上角的三角：</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"446\" src=\"image\\86db7f3caa234aad8ac3f8981f7e4535.png\" width=\"840\"/></p>\n<p> 然后下面就运行成功了......</p>\n<p>吗？</p>\n<p>据我了解大部分人都不会那么顺利，会遇到奇奇怪怪的问题，别怕！往下看。</p>\n<p></p>\n<h2 id=\"%E7%84%B6%E5%90%8E%E5%BE%88%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%BA%E8%BF%98%E6%98%AF%E4%BC%9A%E4%B8%8D%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%EF%BC%8C%E5%88%AB%E6%80%95%EF%BC%81\"><strong>会遇到的问题</strong></h2>\n<p>很多人会遇到这两个问题：</p>\n<h3 id=\"1.%23include%E6%8A%A5%E9%94%99%EF%BC%8C%E6%89%BE%E4%B8%8D%E5%88%B0%E5%A4%B4%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E3%80%82\"><strong>1.#include报错，找不到头文件。</strong></h3>\n<p>解决方法：配置编译器路径，按快捷键Ctrl+Shift+P调出命令面板，输入C/C++，选择“Edit Configurations(UI)”进入配置，选定你的编译器，比如我的就是“D:\\aaakkk\\cpp\\mingw64\\bin\\c++.exe”，还有在IntelliSense 模式选定“windows-gcc-x64”</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"1029\" src=\"image\\47aaddfef75d4f978229ccf5043ba4b7.png\" width=\"1200\"/></p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<h3 id=\"%C2%A02.%E2%80%9Cg%2B%2B%20%3A%20%E6%97%A0%E6%B3%95%E5%B0%86%E2%80%9Cg%2B%2B%E2%80%9D%E9%A1%B9%E8%AF%86%E5%88%AB%E4%B8%BA%20cmdlet%E3%80%81%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E3%80%81%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E6%88%96%E5%8F%AF%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%E7%9A%84%E5%90%8D%E7%A7%B0%E3%80%82%E2%80%9D\"><strong> 2.“g++ : 无法将“g++”项识别为 cmdlet、函数、脚本文件或可运行程序的名称。”</strong></h3>\n<p>解决方法：如果确保你的环境变量没配错，那就要用管理员权限打开VSCode：右键VScode-属性-兼容性-勾选以管理员身份运行此程序。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" height=\"759\" src=\"image\\18af24151ba545b6a5fabe61c4834329.png\" width=\"539\"/></p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n</div>\n</div>"}